        function renderProducts(filter = 'todos', searchTerm = '') {
            const container = document.getElementById('productsContainer');
            
            let filtered = products;
            if (filter !== 'todos') {
                filtered = products.filter(p => p.category === filter);
            }
            if (searchTerm) {
                filtered = filtered.filter(p => 
                    p.name.toLowerCase().includes(searchTerm.toLowerCase()) ||
                    p.targets.toLowerCase().includes(searchTerm.toLowerCase()) ||
                    p.actives.toLowerCase().includes(searchTerm.toLowerCase())
                );
            }

            const categories = {
                bionematicida: { title: 'BIONEMATICIDAS', icon: 'fa-shield-virus' },
                biofungicida: { title: 'BIOFUNGICIDAS', icon: 'fa-bacteria' },
                bioinseticida: { title: 'BIOINSETICIDAS', icon: 'fa-bug' },
                fisiologico: { title: 'DESTAQUES FISIOL√ìGICOS', icon: 'fa-sun' },
                inoculante: { title: 'INOCULANTES', icon: 'fa-dna' }
            };

            let html = '';
            Object.keys(categories).forEach(catKey => {
                const catProducts = filtered.filter(p => p.category === catKey);
                if (catProducts.length > 0) {
                    html += `
                        <section class="mb-12">
                            <div class="category-title">
                                <i class="fas ${categories[catKey].icon}"></i>
                                ${categories[catKey].title}
                            </div>
                            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                                ${catProducts.map(p => `
                                    <div class="product-card" style="border-top-color: ${p.color}">
                                        <div class="p-6">
                                            <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-4">
                                                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">${p.name}</h3>
                                                <span class="bg-gray-100 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-bold" style="color: ${p.color}">
                                                    ${p.badge}
                                                </span>
                                            </div>
                                            
                                            <div class="space-y-3 text-sm">
                                                <div>
                                                    <span class="info-label" style="color: ${p.color}">
                                                        <i class="fas fa-flask"></i> Ativos
                                                    </span>
                                                    <p class="text-gray-700">${p.actives}</p>
                                                </div>
                                                
                                                <div>
                                                    <span class="info-label" style="color: ${p.color}">
                                                        <i class="fas fa-crosshairs"></i> Alvos
                                                    </span>
                                                    <p class="text-gray-700">${p.targets}</p>
                                                </div>
                                                
                                                <div>
                                                    <span class="info-label" style="color: ${p.color}">
                                                        <i class="fas fa-cogs"></i> Modo de A√ß√£o
                                                    </span>
                                                    <p class="text-gray-700">${p.action}</p>
                                                </div>
                                                
                                                <div>
                                                    <span class="info-label" style="color: ${p.color}">
                                                        <i class="fas fa-star"></i> Vantagens
                                                    </span>
                                                    <p class="text-gray-700">${p.advantages}</p>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>

                                            <div class="info-box mt-4">
                                                <span class="info-label">
                                                    <i class="fas fa-tint"></i> Dosagem Recomendada
                                                </span>
                                                <p class="text-sm text-gray-800 font-semibold">${p.dosage}</p>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                `).join('')}
                            </div>
                        </section>
                    `;
                }
            });

            container.innerHTML = html || '<p class="text-center text-gray-500 text-xl">Nenhum produto encontrado</p>';
        }

        function filterCategory(category) {
            currentFilter = category;
            document.querySelectorAll('.filter-btn').forEach(btn => btn.classList.remove('active'));
            event.target.classList.add('active');
            renderProducts(category, document.getElementById('searchInput').value);
        }

        document.getElementById('searchInput').addEventListener('input', (e) => {
            renderProducts(currentFilter, e.target.value);
        });

        // Initialize
        renderProducts();
